## Common Test Scenarios

### ✓ Happy Path
- Create resource with valid data → 201 Created
- Get existing resource → 200 OK
- Update resource → 204 No Content
- Delete resource → 204 No Content

### ✗ Error Cases
- Get non-existent resource → 404 Not Found
- Create with invalid foreign key → 400 Bad Request
- Create with negative values → 400 Bad Request
- Invalid state transition → 400 Bad Request

### 🔄 Business Logic
- Order decreases available portions
- Meal deactivation (not deletion)
- Order state transitions validated
- Menu filtering by date

