## Test File Structure

Each test follows AAA pattern:
```csharp
[Fact]
public async Task TestName()
{
    // Arrange - Setup test data
    var createDto = new { name = "Test" };
    var content = new StringContent(...);

    // Act - Execute endpoint
    var response = await _httpClient.PostAsync("/endpoint", content);

    // Assert - Verify response
    response.StatusCode.Should().Be(HttpStatusCode.Created);
}
```

---

## Database Reset

Automatic before each test class:
```csharp
await _httpClient.PostAsync("/reset-database", null);
```

This endpoint:
1. ✓ Deletes all data
2. ✓ Recreates schema
3. ✓ Seeds test data (2 meals, 2 menu items, 2 orders)

